to lose a son?

216
00:23:28,759 --> 00:23:32,040
What cause can be more
important than human life?

217
00:23:32,079 --> 00:23:36,200
What war can be greater than peace?

218
00:23:38,359 --> 00:23:38,359
l came here because l want to
live like a human being...

219
