520
00:53:36,760 --> 00:53:40,600
lt's beneath us, Kado.

521
00:53:49,679 --> 00:53:50,600
Mamo.

522
00:54:29,800 --> 00:54:30,680
Kado...

523
00:54:33,880 --> 00:54:34,960
Brother!

524
00:54:58,639 --> 00:54:58,639
